<li id="cite_note-slant-26"><b><a href="#cite_ref-slant_26-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFAntani_J">Antani J. <a href="http://www.slantmagazine.com/film/film_review.asp?ID=1080" class="external text" title="http://www.slantmagazine.com/film/film_review.asp?ID=1080" rel="nofollow">"Charulata"</a>. Slant magazine<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.slantmagazine.com/film/film_review.asp?ID=1080" class="external free" title="http://www.slantmagazine.com/film/film_review.asp?ID=1080" rel="nofollow">http://www.slantmagazine.com/film/film_review.asp?ID=1080</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-06-19</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Charulata&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Antani+J&amp;rft.au=Antani+J&amp;rft.pub=Slant+magazine&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.slantmagazine.com%2Ffilm%2Ffilm_review.asp%3FID%3D1080&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Satyajit_Ray"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
