<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20060104143026/http://www.britishcouncil.org/india-connecting-august2005-westindia-satyajit-ray.htm" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20060104143026/http://www.britishcouncil.org/india-connecting-august2005-westindia-satyajit-ray.htm" rel="nofollow">"Satyajit Ray: A Vision of Cinema"</a>. Archived from <a href="http://www.britishcouncil.org/india-connecting-august2005-westindia-satyajit-ray.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.britishcouncil.org/india-connecting-august2005-westindia-satyajit-ray.htm" rel="nofollow">the original</a> on 2006-01-04<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20060104143026/http://www.britishcouncil.org/india-connecting-august2005-westindia-satyajit-ray.htm" class="external free" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20060104143026/http://www.britishcouncil.org/india-connecting-august2005-westindia-satyajit-ray.htm" rel="nofollow">http://web.archive.org/web/20060104143026/http://www.britishcouncil.org/india-connecting-august2005-westindia-satyajit-ray.htm</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Satyajit+Ray%3A+A+Vision+of+Cinema&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20060104143026%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.britishcouncil.org%2Findia-connecting-august2005-westindia-satyajit-ray.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Satyajit_Ray"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> article by <a href="/wiki/Andrew_Robinson_(author)" title="Andrew Robinson (author)" class="mw-redirect">Andrew Robinson</a></li>
