<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;;background-color:#ecd9d9;;border:none;; font-size:xx-small;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Works_of_Satyajit_Ray" title="Template:Works of Satyajit Ray"><span title="View this template" style=";background-color:#ecd9d9;;border:none;">v</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Works_of_Satyajit_Ray&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Template talk:Works of Satyajit Ray (page does not exist)"><span title="Discussion about this template" style=";background-color:#ecd9d9;;border:none;">d</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Works_of_Satyajit_Ray&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Works_of_Satyajit_Ray&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";background-color:#ecd9d9;;border:none;;">e</span></a></div>
