astri</a> (1966)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Indira_Gandhi" title="Indira Gandhi">Indira Gandhi</a> (1971)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/V._V._Giri" title="V. V. Giri">V. V. Giri</a> (1975)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/K._Kamaraj" title="K. Kamaraj">K. Kamaraj</a> (1976)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Mother_Teresa" title="Mother Teresa">Mother Teresa</a> (1980)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Vinoba_Bhave" title="Vinoba Bhave">Acharya Vinoba Bhave</a> (1983)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Khan_Abdul_Ghaffar_Khan" title="Khan Abdul Ghaffar Khan">Khan Abdul Ghaffar Khan</a> (1987)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/M._G._Ramachandran" title="M. G. Ramachandran">M. G. Ramachandran</a> (1988)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/B._R._Ambedkar" title="B. R. Ambedkar">B. R. Ambedkar</a> (1990)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Nelson_Mandela" title="Nelson Mandela">Nelson Mandela</a> (1990)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Rajiv_Gandhi" title="Rajiv Gandhi">Rajiv Gandhi</a> (1991)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sardar_Vallabhbhai_Patel" title="Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel">Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel</a> (1991)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Morarji_Desai" title="Morarji Desai">Morarji Desai</a> (1991)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Abul_Kalam_Azad" title="Abul Kalam Azad">Abul Kalam Azad</a> (1992)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/J._R._D._Tata" title="J. R. D. Tata">J. R. D. Tata</a> (1992)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><strong class="selfli